{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/StorepageHeader1.png?t=1739212132\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are a member of the exploration and investigation team. Your job is to collect enough evidence about the monster that has attacked the station.  Venture across derelict stations and planets. Find a way to survive monster's attacks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/takeSpectralAnalysis.gif?t=1739212132\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/StorepageHeader2.png?t=1739212132\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remember that biomorphs can corrupt one of your team members into working on their side! Beware betrayal! As a corrupted player you are on the quest to disrupt and trick other players into thinking that it's another type of a monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/toiletFlush.gif?t=1739212132\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Other players can vote against suspicious player. Enough votes will result in quick and painless death. <br>Keep your friends close, but enemies even closer!  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/krolikCorruptedLaugh.gif?t=1739212132\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/StorepageHeader3.png?t=1739212132\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Identify more than 20 monster types with unique traits and personalities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/emp5.gif?t=1739212132\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More than 5 maps available for exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/repairElectricalGen2.gif?t=1739212132\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience immersion with realistic graphics, high interactivity and fine tuned sounds. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/toiletscreamer2.gif?t=1739212132\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your voice is recognized and understood by the monster and can even be stolen and used against your team!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 difficulties including custom one to tailor your own experience.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Space is Deep and Dark place to go alone. So, bring friends, or join open lobbies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/extras/dance.gif?t=1739212132\" /></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739212132","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/page.bg.jpg?t=1739212132","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/4b105263efef880b786139f9f473e3b86c4ab641/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739212132","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541520/4b105263efef880b786139f9f473e3b86c4ab641/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739212132","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"des